---
// About Component — Optimized
---

<section id="about" class="py-20 lg:py-32 bg-white px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto flex flex-col-reverse lg:flex-row items-center gap-12 lg:gap-20">
    
    <!-- Text Content -->
    <div class="w-full lg:w-1/2 flex flex-col items-center lg:items-start text-center lg:text-left reveal-right">
      <!-- Badge pill -->
      <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-accent/15 text-choco/80 text-sm font-body font-semibold px-5 py-2 rounded-full mb-6">
        ✨ Conoce a la chef
      </span>

      <!-- Main heading -->
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-brand font-bold mb-8">
        <span class="text-choco">Hola, soy </span><span class="text-cta">Faty</span>
      </h2>
      
      <div class="bg-cream p-8 rounded-[2rem] shadow-sm border border-accent/20 relative">
        <!-- SVG Quote icon -->
        <svg class="absolute top-6 left-6 w-10 h-10 text-accent/50 -translate-x-4 -translate-y-4" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M14.017 21v-7.391c0-5.704 3.731-9.57 8.983-10.609l.995 2.151c-2.432.917-3.995 3.638-3.995 5.849h4v10h-9.983zm-14.017 0v-7.391c0-5.704 3.748-9.57 9-10.609l.996 2.151c-2.433.917-3.996 3.638-3.996 5.849h3.983v10h-9.983z"/></svg>
        
        <p class="text-lg text-choco/80 font-body leading-relaxed relative z-10 mb-4">
          PastelArte nació en la estufa de mi casa, horneando con amor para las personas que más quiero. 
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg text-choco/80 font-body leading-relaxed relative z-10">
          Mi misión es simple: transformar ingredientes premium en momentos de felicidad pura. ¡Esa sensación de cerrar los ojos al probar algo delicioso es la magia que horneo para ti cada día! ✨
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-8 flex gap-4" aria-hidden="true">
        <!-- Decorative sparkle elements using <use> -->
        <svg viewBox="0 0 100 100" class="w-8 h-8 fill-accent rotate-12"><use href="#sparkle" /></svg>
        <svg viewBox="0 0 100 100" class="w-8 h-8 fill-cta -rotate-12"><use href="#sparkle" /></svg>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Image Polaroid -->
    <div class="w-full lg:w-1/2 mb-10 lg:mb-0 relative reveal-left flex justify-center">
      <div class="relative w-11/12 max-w-sm bg-white p-4 pb-14 rounded-md shadow-2xl rotate-3 hover:rotate-0 transition-transform duration-500 z-10">
        <img 
          src="/images/conoceme.webp" 
          alt="Faty, la chef y fundadora de PastelArte, sonriendo en su cocina" 
          class="w-full aspect-[4/5] object-cover rounded-sm border border-gray-100"
          loading="lazy"
        />
        <div class="absolute bottom-4 left-0 w-full text-center font-brand text-choco/60 text-lg rotate-[-2deg]">
          Horneando felicidad ✨
        </div>
      </div>
      <!-- Decorative background -->
      <div class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-[120%] h-[120%] bg-accent/20 rounded-full blur-3xl -z-10" aria-hidden="true"></div>
    </div>
    
  </div>
</section>
